OL,3,CArsonist admits barber shop fire which
OL,4,Cleft four in hospital
OL,6,FAn arsonist has admitted he intended
OL,7,Fto put lives at risk when he started a
OL,8,Fbarber shop blaze that left four
OL,9,Fpeople in hospital including one man
OL,10,Fwho had been "on fire".
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to
OL,13,FAmed's Hair Design, on Stamfordham
OL,14,FRoad, in the West End of Newcastle,
OL,15,Fshortly after 10am on May 23 last year.
OL,17,FThe Great North Air Ambulance also
OL,18,Fattended and four people were taken to
OL,19,Fhospital, two with serious injuries.
