OL,3,CArsonist admits barber shop fire which
OL,4,Cleft four in hospital
OL,6,FDilovan Sindi, 40, of Sulgrave Road,
OL,7,FWashington, Tyne and Wear, initially
OL,8,Ffaced attempted murder charges.
OL,10,FHowever, just before his trial was due
OL,11,Fto start at Newcastle Crown Court on
OL,12,FWednesday (25 September), he pleaded
OL,13,Fguilty to arson with intent to
OL,14,Fendanger life, attempted wounding and
OL,15,Fcausing grievous bodily harm, which
OL,16,Fprosecutors accepted.
OL,18,FNo further details about what happened
OL,19,Fwere given during the hearing or what
OL,20,Fmotivation was behind the blaze.
