OL,6,FSindi will be sentenced in December
OL,7,Fand has been remanded in custody.
OL,9,FJudge Robert Adams said: "It is
OL,10,Finevitably a custodial sentence, of
OL,11,Fsome length."
OL,13,FPictures taken at the scene show
OL,14,Fforensic teams and police outside the
OL,15,Fshop.
OL,17,FOne local, who wished to remain
OL,18,Fanonymous, said on the day he had been
OL,19,Fout walking his dog when he came
OL,20,Facross a man on fire outside the
OL,21,Fburning shop.
