OL,3,CArsonist admits barber shop fire which
OL,4,Cleft four in hospital
OL,6,FHe said: "I was walking my dog nearby
OL,7,Fwhen I saw three people coming out of
OL,8,Fthe barbers.
OL,10,F"They seemed to come out but then they
OL,11,Fwanted to go back in. I thought there
OL,12,Fmust have been a fight inside.
OL,14,F"All of a sudden there was smoke from
OL,15,Fthe barbers and about two minutes
OL,16,Flater the guy came 20 yards away from
OL,17,Fthe shop.
OL,19,F"As he got nearer you could tell he
OL,20,Fwas on fire. It was really bad.
