OL,4,Cleft four in hospital
OL,6,F"I started shouting for him to get on
OL,7,Fthe ground. I ran onto the road and
OL,8,Ftried to pat the fire out. I was
OL,9,Fpatting him with one hand and had my
OL,10,Fdog in the other.
OL,12,F"A lady managed to get hold of a
OL,13,Fblanket but the real hero of the day
OL,14,Fwas a truck driver who had a fire
OL,15,Fextinguisher with him. He just
OL,16,Fhappened to be passing."
