OL,3,CArsonist admits barber shop fire which
OL,4,Cleft four in hospital
OL,6,FThe man added: "It was so out of the
OL,7,Fblue. I couldn't believe my eyes. It
OL,8,Ftook me 20 seconds to process what was
OL,9,Fhappening. When I did realise what was
OL,10,Fgoing on I tried to help as best as I
OL,11,Fcould.
OL,13,F"I could also hear someone else
OL,14,Fshouting from inside the shop while
OL,15,Fthis was all going on. I got the
OL,16,Fimpression this person was trapped
OL,17,Finside the barbers.
OL,19,F"He did eventually come out when the
OL,20,Femergency services were here but he
OL,21,Flooked burned too."
